                        <condition key="deficient">The binding might originally belong to a
                           different codex.
 The leather cover is damaged, partly missing.
                           The leather cover is cut off at the spine.
 The red ink is faded,
                           rubricated passages are barely legible, s. <locus from="1r" to="47v">1r-47v</locus>.
 Several fols. are of smaller size, fols. 2, 3,
                           6, 7, 18, 19, 22, 23, 26, 31, 33, 36, 37, 40, 42, 43, 44, 45.
 Some
                           fols. are stained and dirty, <locus target="#24v">24v</locus>, 25r,
                           50r.</condition>
