               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0216MGM">Mǝʾǝsar Gʷǝḥila Qǝddus Mikāʾel / MGM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1915" notAfter="1918">King Mikāʾel (Mikāʾel ʿAli of Wällo;
                        d. 1918) and Metropolitan Ṗeṭros (in tenure 1881-1917) are mentioned in the
                        colophon.</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Several names are mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas, some are partly illegible, Ṣǝge Dǝngǝl (6vb, 16vb, 45ra), Kidāna Māryām (68vb), Walatta Kidān (53va, 69rb),
                     Walatta Haywät (16vb, 55va, 61vb), Walatta Madḫǝn
                        (11rb, 59va).</provenance></history>
